==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: oversimplify
<hw>oversimplify</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to simplify excessively so
as to distort or misrepresent; -- of facts, assertions, or
communications; <as>as, Don't <ex>oversimplify</ex> the
rules</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> make too simple.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oversize</ent>⟦br⟧
